Witcher 4 Gameplay FIRST LOOK - Tech Demo PS5
In this Witcher 4 video, we're going to be taking a look at the Unreal Engine 5 tech demo of The Witcher 4 that was revealed at the state of Unreal about a day ago now, we're going to get into what we learned from that, What the Witcher 4 is shaping up to be, what we've gleaned from the 15-minute presentation there, and just get into the details of that.
